### Variables Globales
@apiUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@companyName = Fábrica Argentina de Motores
@adminName = Matías Lorenzo
@emailAdmin = matias@motoresarg.com
@passwordAdmin = password123
@taxId = 20-30456789-2
@address = Av. General Paz 1234, CABA
@newName = Motores Argentinos S.A
@operarioName = Operario Juan
@operarioEmail = juan@motoresarg.com
@operarioPassword = operariopassword

### 1. REGISTRO MAESTRO (Crear Empresa + Admin Owner)
# @name registerMaster
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/register-company
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "companyName": "{{companyName}}",
  "adminName": "{{adminName}}",
  "email": "{{emailAdmin}}",
  "password": "{{passwordAdmin}}"
}


### 2. LOGIN DEL ADMIN (Para obtener el Token)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{emailAdmin}}",
  "password": "{{passwordAdmin}}"
}

###
@tokenAdmin = {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}


### 3. OBTENER PERFIL DE LA EMPRESA
# Verifica que el middleware 'isCompanyOwner' permita el acceso
GET {{apiUrl}}/company/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}


### 4. ACTUALIZAR DATOS DE LA EMPRESA
# Cambiamos dirección y taxId (CUIT)
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/company/update
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "taxId": "{{taxId}}",
  "address": "{{address}}",
  "name": "{{newName}}"
}

### 5a. REGISTRAR UN OPERARIO (Como el ADMIN de la empresa)
# @name registerOperario
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/register
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{operarioName}}",
  "email": "{{operarioEmail}}",
  "password": "{{operarioPassword}}",
  "role": "OPERARIO"  
}

### 5b. LOGIN DEL OPERARIO
# @name loginOperario
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{operarioEmail}}",
  "password": "{{operarioPassword}}"
}

###
@tokenOperario = {{loginOperario.response.body.token}}


### 5c. INTENTO DE ACCESO AL PERFIL (Debe fallar con 403)
# El Operario pertenece a la empresa, pero NO es el Owner.
GET {{apiUrl}}/company/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenOperario}}

### 6. DESACTIVAR EMPRESA (Borrado Lógico)
# Esto marca 'active: false'. Útil para bajas de suscripción.
PATCH {{apiUrl}}/company/deactivate
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}